#. Dgf7D
#: 06050000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06050000.xhp\n"
"par_id3155922\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_INSWIN_INPUT\">Enter the formula that you want to add to the current cell. You can also click the <link href=\"text/scalc/01/04060000.xhp\">Function Wizard</link> icon to insert a predefined function into the formula.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_INSWIN_INPUT\">ປ້ອນສູດທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເພີ່ມໃສ່ເຊວປະຈຸບັນ. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດຄລິກໄອຄອນ <link href=\"text/scalc/01/04060000.xhp\">ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງຟັງຊັນ</link> ເພື່ອແຊກຟັງຊັນທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ລ່ວງໜ້າເຂົ້າໃນສູດ.</ahelp>"

