"par_id3153823\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_INSWIN_CANCEL\">Clears the contents of the <emph>Input line</emph>, or cancels the changes that you made to an existing formula.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_INSWIN_CANCEL\">ລຶບເນື້ອໃນຂອງ <emph>ແຖວປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນ</emph>, ຫຼື ຍົກເລີກການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ເຮັດກັບສູດທີ່ມີຢູ່.</ahelp>"

#. DjEeK
#: 06060000.xhp
msgctxt ""
